10.10
\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution*
\paragraph_spacing double
(a) The log density is 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\log f\left(x\mid\theta\right)=\log\theta-\theta x
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution*
\paragraph_spacing double
The second derivative of the log density is
